title: I AM NASCAR: Erik Moses
description:
WATCH MORE → https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=70YdJ...

I AM NASCAR | SEASON 2: EPISODE 13

Brandon Marshall, Channing Crowder and  Dion “Rocko” Williams Link up with Erik Moses, president of Nashville Superspeedway, Dover Motorsports, Inc. in episode 13 of I AM NASCAR.  The five discuss improving diversity in NASCAR and what it's going to take to grow its audience.
